1. *Ispočetka* ću naučiti gramatiku srpskog jezika. (I will learn Serbian grammar *from scratch*.)
2. Nismo imali dovoljno vremena pa smo morali da počnemo *ispočetka*. (We didn't have enough time so we had to start *all over again*.)
3. Moramo da razmislimo o ovome *ispočetka*. (We have to rethink this *from the beginning*.)
4. *Ispočetka* sam čitao ovu knjigu tri puta. (I read this book three times *from the beginning*.)
5. Kada smo shvatili da smo napravili grešku, odlučili smo da krenemo *ispočetka*. (When we realized we made a mistake, we decided to start *from scratch*.)

Note: In Serbian, the word "ispočetka" means "from the beginning" or "from scratch" and it can be used in various forms and positions in a sentence depending on the context. The sentences above showcase some of the most common ways it can be used. The * symbol is used to highlight the word in each sentence.